GeneralComments:
5 am to 3 pm 7 days a week
Charge up while you enjoy great café food and coffee. 30 Amp Delta EV chargepoint for Kopu Café customers. Please ask for the charger to be switched on when you order. There is a $2.50 per hour charge, please pay when you order. This charger is for customers only. NOTE: There is no charging after 3 pm. When coming from Auckland turn left onto slip road immediately after the bridge or sharp left at the Kopu roundabout. If you fancy a stroll or you have your bike, the Rail trail is nearby.
